{"tid":1286621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"利用武漢事件","createTime":"2019-07-05T02:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T03:39:37.000Z","uid":215225,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"59b54ee3e6c46e87d03d728fb96dfa600ecdb2fc","tid":1286621,"uid":215225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f224d6e0aa24350be4e442ef7da3b7ab686c597","tid":1286621,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:15:08.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b9d040cf688f55cf8f2cce6fda8c1a7671a4715","tid":1286621,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:22:25.000Z","msg":"agree, 問題係點樣唔失焦, 先唔好自己設限俾自己<br />\n再退一步諗, 實有人想理有人唔想理, 理嗰啲人低調唔好嗌出口, 淨係派吓傳單順便要佢哋關注人權問題又得唔得?<br />\n<br />\n鄰國人冇錯成日都有關我撚事心態, 但係都有維權既人㗎嘛, 唔會咁快唔記得掛?<br />\n<br />\n最後, 尊重民意, 我哋可以喺度傾喺到拉攏, 但係鬼會take risk去搞自己人權問題? 唔好玩啦"},{"pid":"2d7073ad3f171c7af4a68853fc16979564d1ccd7","tid":1286621,"uid":127751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ee69cb38a20839e86067dca1b90986b7b729fb","tid":1286621,"uid":258706,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:31:05.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各有各做啦<br />\n連登撑同唔撑聲緩武漢嘅人都有<br />\n依家最驚7.7內訌<br />\n好怕舉牌聲援武漢嗰啲俾覺得只應該有反送中標語出街嘅人當場鬧同嘈交<br />\n繼而俾位人入同失焦<br />\n大家7.7出嚟嗰陣，對武漢咩立場都好，所有人都係有份反送中<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家互相尊重，勿分化，不內訌</span>"},{"pid":"c5936b6f65cbcd1a5bb0e766c9eb2ab813a32dc2","tid":1286621,"uid":215225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:11:27.000Z","msg":"負皮嗰D出黎講兩句啦<br />\n成日話兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n原來對於分歧就用負評+block黎解決<br />\n點解唔用道理黎說服人哋"},{"pid":"3637d913f94cd5339f75b35448864aa002a8f15f","tid":1286621,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:19:26.000Z","msg":"想問7/7後<br />\nSet幾時做deadline?<br />\n冇deadline好難凝聚人"},{"pid":"b12c91382ebf66fd940c5d8b0cf561d80d55ec86","tid":1286621,"uid":56157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5936b6f65cbcd1a5bb0e766c9eb2ab813a32dc2","tid":1286621,"uid":215225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:11:27.000Z","msg":"負皮嗰D出黎講兩句啦<br />\n成日話兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n原來對於分歧就用負評+block黎解決<br />\n點解唔用道理黎說服人哋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山各自努力係講緊爬緊同一座山<br />\n即係有相同目的（反送中以及相關訴求）但唔會因為不因其手段（勇武/和理非）而割席<br />\n<br />\n武漢已經係第二座山。唔係爬同一座山點解要支持你？<br />\n<br />\n再講你點解唔叫武漢人支持返香港反送中訴求？"},{"pid":"2e70c4b5b21ea66b4358e289aaddba89f0d765d8","tid":1286621,"uid":215225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b12c91382ebf66fd940c5d8b0cf561d80d55ec86","tid":1286621,"uid":56157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5936b6f65cbcd1a5bb0e766c9eb2ab813a32dc2","tid":1286621,"uid":215225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:11:27.000Z","msg":"負皮嗰D出黎講兩句啦<br />\n成日話兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n原來對於分歧就用負評+block黎解決<br />\n點解唔用道理黎說服人哋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山各自努力係講緊爬緊同一座山<br />\n即係有相同目的（反送中以及相關訴求）但唔會因為不因其手段（勇武/和理非）而割席<br />\n<br />\n武漢已經係第二座山。唔係爬同一座山點解要支持你？<br />\n<br />\n再講你點解唔叫武漢人支持返香港反送中訴求？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:38:14.000Z